				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Below are the details to the location of the camp and the tatics/pets used.
<br />

<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Zone:</span> <a href="http://eqatlas.com/ykesha/cryptofnadoxmap.html" target="_blank" class="postlink">Crypt of Nadox</a>
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Camp:</span> Furious/Vehement Room
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Pet:</span> Ward of Xegony (unfocused)
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Gear:</span> Bazaar geared mage (FT1, 1700hp, 3200 mana pool, SCM 3)
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Specialization:</span> Evocation
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Outside Buffs:</span> KEI
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Location:</span> This is assuming you know how to get to the lighthouse in Gunthak.Increase your fire resists, invis up and run South out over the water to the beach. Hugging the West wall of the Beach take your first right into the cave. Continue following the cave and take your second left. Take your next right and you will soon zone into Nadox. Once you enter Nadox, run through the lava until you see the bridge overhead. Go up on the ledge just before the bridge. Once you are on solid ground hang a left and follow the lava river (on your left) to the wall. This is 100% safe unless mobs are pulled here. This is where you prep and get your pet ready.
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Tactic used:</span> 
<br />
1. Pull mob with Malisement
<br />
2. Start casting Fire Bolt of Tallon when mob hits 80%
<br />
3. Start casting Fire Bolt of Tallon when mob hits 40%
<br />
4. When mob is dead let pet regen back up to full hps then kill next (This also gives you time to med mana). You may need to throw in a heal on the Blackhand Lieutenants or named, especially if they are dual wielding (you will see to weapons).
<br />
<span style="font-weight: bold">Mobs:</span>
<br />
<a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=11152" target="_blank" class="postlink">A Blackhand Guardian</a> (about 8000hp, max hits around 150)
<br />
.....<span style="font-style: italic">Loot:</span>
<br />
........1. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=20487" target="_blank" class="postlink">Corroded Pick Hilt</a> 9pp to vendor
<br />
........2. Weapons 5pp to vendor
<br />
........3. Various low end gems between 9pp and 47pp to vendors
<br />
........4. Various research pages and runes
<br />
<a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=11151" target="_blank" class="postlink">A Soot Covered Miner</a> (about 7000hp, max hits around 140)
<br />
.....<span style="font-style: italic">Loot:</span>
<br />
........1. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=20487" target="_blank" class="postlink">Corroded Pick Hilt</a> 9pp to vendor
<br />
........2. Weapons 5pp to vendor
