........5. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19981" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ornate Miner's Pick</a> 47pp to vendor
<br />
........6. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19382" target="_blank" class="postlink">Gem Pouch</a> 30% item and coin reduction
<br />
<a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=14170" target="_blank" class="postlink">An Exhaused Miner</a> (about 7000hp, max hits around 140)
<br />
.....<span style="font-style: italic">Loot:</span>
