........4. Various research pages and runes
<br />
........5. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19981" target="_blank" class="postlink">Ornate Miner's Pick</a> 47pp to vendor
<br />
<a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=11659" target="_blank" class="postlink">An Exhausted Bloodtusk</a> (about 12000hp, max hits around 180, enrages)
<br />
.....<span style="font-style: italic">Loot:</span>
<br />
........1. High end research pages and runes
<br />
........2. High end gems
<br />
........3. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19425" target="_blank" class="postlink">Boar Snout Ring</a>
