<br />
........5. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19345" target="_blank" class="postlink">Broken Skull Clan Blood</a> used for priest quest
<br />
........6. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19214" target="_blank" class="postlink">Hate Forged Pauldrons</a>
<br />
<a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=11163" target="_blank" class="postlink">A Vehement Blackhand</a> (about 5400hp, max hits around 140)
<br />
.....<span style="font-style: italic">Loot:</span>
<br />
........1. Weapons 5pp to vendor
<br />
........2. Various low end gems between 9pp and 47pp to vendors
<br />
........3. Various research pages and runes
<br />
........4. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19430" target="_blank" class="postlink">A Dark Ore Amulet</a> used for melee quest
<br />
........5. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19345" target="_blank" class="postlink">Broken Skull Clan Blood</a> used for priest quest
