........6. <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=19214" target="_blank" class="postlink">Hate Forged Pauldrons</a>
<br />
<a href="http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=11136" target="_blank" class="postlink">A Blackhand Lieutenant</a> (about 8000hp, max hits around 150)
